    "Table A comparison of Random Forest and LASSO models trained on text-based features (Keywords, CTMs, and sentence clusters) against a median baseline Random Forest LASSO RMSE, % MAE, % RMSE, % MAE, % Baseline 2.33 1.30 2.33 1.30 Keywords 2.12 -8.85** 1.25 -4.20* 2.33 0.10 1.32 0.88 CTMs 2.09 -10.12* 1.24 -4.87* 2.19 -5.90** 1.27 -2.44* Sentence clusters 2.22 -4.75 1.29 -1.05 2.18 -6.23* 1.28 -1.59",
